column2: SELECT      p.objID, f.id as FIRST_ID, f.ra as FIRST_ra, f.dec as FIRST_dec, p.ra as SDSS_ra, p.dec as SDSS_dec, p.type,      pz.objID, pz.z, pz.zErr,      s.specObjID, s.bestObjID, s.z, s.zErr, s.sourcetype, s.class, s.subClass,         gl.h_alpha_eqw,       gl.h_alpha_flux into mydb.New from MyDB.FIRST_Reduced_#p0#deg AS f    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(f.ra, f.dec, #) AS x     JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON x.objID = p.objID    LEFT JOIN PhotoZ pz ON p.objID = pz.objID    LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID    LEFT JOIN GalSpecLine gl ON s.specobjid = gl.specobjid
